<body>
    <h1>Workflow</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 id=3D"Workflow-WorkflowFramework">Workflow Framework</h1>
<p><a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"http://wiki/index.php/Image:WorkflowT=
ables.png" rel=3D"nofollow">http://wiki/index.php/Image:WorkflowTables.png<=
/a><br>
 The workflow ERD shows the basic relationships among tables supporting wor=
kflow.<br>
 Requisitions and purchase orders move through workflow to get their approp=
riate approvals and get distributed as needed. Workflow configuration is pe=
rformed by uploading a set of folders (some of which may be processed by ro=
bots) and a specification of the relationships among steps, activities, and=
 folders.</p>
<p>Alexey made an introduction video here:&nbsp;\\Scifile\Departments\Devel=
opment\Training\Workflow (Workflow.mpg) which goes through an example workf=
low and describes relationships among the various objects. Other files in t=
hat folder may also be helpful in understanding workflow.</p>
<p>The DTD for workflow configuration (http://cvs.sciquest.com/viewcvs/view=
cvs.cgi/*checkout*/applications/docs/dtd/workflow/WorkflowDefinition.dtd) m=
ay help clarify some issues about exactly what goes in a workflow definitio=
n file.</p>
<p>Workflow changes in 9.3 are documented <a class=3D"external-link" href=
=3D"http://wiki/images/c/c3/Workflow_Improvements_9.3.pptx" rel=3D"nofollow=
">here (ppt)</a></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
